<item>
            <title>[LU-12670] osd_oxc_get(): Shrink rcu critical section to not include EXIT</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12670</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;osd_oxc_get() has a quirk where ENTRY / EXIT may be unbalanced with respect to the out: label.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In addition when CDEBUG() is enabled EXIT the macro trace is included in the rcu critical section. Move EXIT outside of the critical section and re-balance the ENTRY/EXIT macros.&lt;br/&gt;
&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
